ikt regnskap gj\u00f8r det n\u00e5 mulig \u00e5 f\u00f8lge utviklingen fra \u00e5r til \u00e5r, og iverksette n\u00f8dvendige tiltak for \u00e5 snu utviklingen vi har sett de siste \u00e5rene, sier Opoku."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "71ff5e096be5c036cce19fb8cd3a2c63d85cd668584c2325d2225dc3f2a2c315"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-01-29T20:53:49.158Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Klimagassutslippene i Trondheim \u00f8ker voldsomt. Bystyret skal lage et \u00e5rlig regnskap for klimafotavtrykket, og p\u00e5 den m\u00e5ten jobbe for \u00e5 snu utviklingen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/trondheim/article10593769.ece/syiwhj/ALTERNATES/w980-default/bystyret7nett_mv.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/80886736580d2d1328fbfbc4b0b80a65bc081fb2.jpg?593fdc2d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Klimagassutslippene i Trondheim skal overv\u00e5kes -adressa.no", "Utslippene \u00f8ker", "Et viktig verkt\u00f8y"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "80886736580d2d1328fbfbc4b0b80a65bc081fb2"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["snu utviklingen", "utslipp", "regnskap", "trondheim", "klimagassutslippene"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["milj\u00f8partiet de gr\u00f8nne", "misa"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value